CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1956, pg. A16 reads: "The Working Scene of the Paree Salon show the new open working arrangements where the beauticians will make milady handsome from nine in morning until ten at night."
TitMainTitle: Interior of Paree Beauty Salon with snake plants, triangular patterned screen, and large amount of floral arrangements for Grand Opening in foreground
